    Q.changed = 1;
}
!}
go-to: changed if changed = 1
on-departure: ideology = "Right-wing Stresemannite"; right_stresemannite_strength += 10; right_stresemannite_dissent -= 10; left_stresemannite_dissent -= 5;

Our party has largely survived thanks to the efforts of our party leader, Gustav Stresemann. With him at the helm, he has consistently shown himself to be an ardent nationalist with a more compromising approach to politics compared to the <span style="color: #3F7BC1;">**DNVP**</span>; emulating his steady yet flexible style of governance will further cement the <span style="color: var(--nlp-color);">**[+ nlp_name +]**</span> as the Party of Reason.

@labor
