The <span style="color: var(--nlp-color);">**[+ nlp_name +]**</span> has had a special mutually beneficial relationship with the classes of industrial magnates and small business owners since its creation, one which has become somewhat strained with Stresemann’s stance of cautious acceptance towards the Weimar Republic. By secretly holding meetings with business owners, and accepting some “gifts” in exchange for policies more favourable for business, we can maintain their trust and funding.

@changed
on-arrival: left_stresemannite_dissent += 5; right_stresemannite_dissent += 5; labor_dissent += 5; industrialist_dissent += 5

We have changed ideologies. Many in the party feel unmoored.
